chatprefs-help:
Chat preference commands:
/chatprefs languagecolors on|off
/chatprefs labels on|off
/chatprefs preset default|highcontrast|coloruniversal|protanopia|deuteranopia|tritanopia|monochrome
/chatprefs langcolor &lt;language&gt; &lt;hex|default&gt;
/chatprefs nickcolors on|off
/chatprefs ooccolor &lt;hex|default&gt;
/chatprefs gooccolor &lt;hex|default&gt;
/chatprefs emotecolor &lt;hex|default&gt;
/chatprefs reset

notes-help-admin:
Staff notes commands:
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; - open staff notes
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; list
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; add &lt;note text&gt;
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; view &lt;id&gt;
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; edit &lt;id&gt; &lt;note text&gt;
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; delete &lt;id&gt; confirm
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; ledger view
/adminnotes &lt;player&gt; ledger set &lt;freeform text&gt;

notes-help-personal:
Private notes commands:
/notes - open your private notes
/notes about &lt;player&gt; - open private notes about another player
/notes list
/notes add &lt;note text&gt;
/notes view &lt;id&gt;
/notes edit &lt;id&gt; &lt;note text&gt;
/notes delete &lt;id&gt; confirm
